data.description: Beautiful, spacious home with plenty of room for the family and entertaining. Large master bedroom with a sitting area perfect for reading, huge walk in closet, master bath offering an over sized shower and Jacuzzi tub. On the main level you will find a large kitchen with island, family room and dining room. Located in the finished basement there is enough room for pool table, watching TV with the family and a full bath. The fenced in backyard has deck and a built in fire pit. All on a cul-de-sac!!! Call this one home.
